OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FPublic Health authorities across the
OL,8,FChannel Islands are warning about the
OL,9,Fthreat of sun damage after recent UV
OL,10,Flevels have been as high as they are
OL,11,Fin August.
OL,13,FIt comes after recent UV readings of 6
OL,14,Fand above - which experts say puts
OL,15,Fpeople at risk of getting caught out
OL,16,Fand sunburnt whilst temperatures are
OL,17,Fnot yet too hot.
OL,19,FThis is because UV levels are
OL,20,Fdetermined by the sun's height in the
OL,21,Fsky, rather than temperature.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FThey are at their maximum during the
OL,8,Fsummer solstice in June, when the sun
OL,9,Fis highest in the sky - but with April
OL,10,Fand August sitting equal distance from
OL,11,Fthe solstice, UV levels can be similar
OL,12,Fduring these months.
OL,14,FPublic Health authorities say this is
OL,15,Fof particular concern in the Channel
OL,16,FIslands, where skin cancer rates are
OL,17,Fabnormally high.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FThe islands' latest Cancer Report
OL,8,Fshowed non-melanoma skin cancers
OL,9,Faccounted for 41 percent of malignant
OL,10,Fcancers in Jersey and 36 percent of
OL,11,Fmalignant cancers in Guernsey between
OL,12,F2020 and 2022.
OL,14,F"Guernsey has incredibly high rates of
OL,15,Fskin cancer - our incidence rate for
OL,16,Fnew malignant melanoma diagnoses in
OL,17,Fthe last cancer report was 95% higher
OL,18,Fthan England's", Diane Mathews,
OL,19,FStrategic Screening Lead for Public
OL,20,FHealth Guernsey, explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,F"In addition, recent statistics from
OL,8,Fthe Guernsey and Alderney Wellbeing
OL,9,FSurvey show that people are being
OL,10,Fsunburned more now than they were ten
OL,11,Fyears ago and know less about the
OL,12,Fearly signs of sun damage."
OL,14,FMartin Knight, Head of Health
OL,15,FImprovement for Public Health Jersey,
OL,16,Fagrees.
OL,18,F"We love to get outside in Jersey and
OL,19,Fthat puts us at an increased risk", he
OL,20,Fexplains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,F"We recognise that we need to have an
OL,8,Fincreased attention to that and when
OL,9,Fwe're looking at skin cancer -
OL,10,Fparticularly those non-malignant skin
OL,11,Fcancers that are preventable - we want
OL,12,Fto detect them earlier when people are
OL,13,Factually finding them."
OL,15,FRhona Hewit discovered a malignant
OL,16,Fmelanoma on her leg two years ago, and
OL,17,Ffurther tests revealed the cancer had
OL,18,Fspread to her lymph nodes.
OL,20,FShe then had to undergo 11 months of
OL,21,Fimmunotherapy treatment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FShe says she feels the dangers of skin
OL,8,Fcancer are too-often overlooked.
OL,10,F"People do kind of think that if you
OL,11,Fhave something - a mole or anything
OL,12,Flike that that's a bit unusual - then
OL,13,Fyou can just have it removed and
OL,14,Fthat's the end of it ", she explains,
OL,15,F"but it's not always the case,
OL,16,Fcertainly not with melanoma.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,F"I still have three-monthly scans and
OL,8,Fthree-monthly bloods and appointments
OL,9,Fwith oncology - and you know as soon
OL,10,Fas those appointments drop, then
OL,11,Fthere's the nerves come back where
OL,12,Fyou're waiting to see if this scan
OL,13,Fwill be clear.
OL,15,F"You're only as good as your last
OL,16,Fscan", she says.
OL,18,FRhona runs a beach cafe and Gorey and
OL,19,Fadds she has already seen several
OL,20,Fclients caught out by the strength of
OL,21,Fthe sun over the past couple of weeks.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,F"At this time of year people
OL,8,Fparticularly don't necessarily pay
OL,9,Fthat much attention", she says, "if
OL,10,Fyou're going to the beach you might
OL,11,Fcover yourself in sun cream in August,
OL,12,Fbut when there's this cool breeze they
OL,13,Fmight not think about it quite so
OL,14,Freadily."
OL,16,FBoth islands' health authorities are
OL,17,Finvesting in skin cancer prevention
OL,18,Fand early detection programmes.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FPublic Health Guernsey have partnered
OL,8,Fwith UK charity 'Skcin' to offer ten
OL,9,Ffree training spaces to hair, beauty,
OL,10,Fand tattoo professionals on a course
OL,11,Fdesigned to teach them to spot the
OL,12,Fearly signs and symptoms of skin
OL,13,Fcancer and signpost clients to medical
OL,14,Fsupport.
OL,16,FPublic Health Jersey are reinvesting
OL,17,Fin their 'sun safe schools' programme
OL,18,Fand are also looking at educating
OL,19,Fprofessionals working in care and
OL,20,Fcosmetics to spot the signs of skin
OL,21,Fcancer early on.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/11
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
