PN,38910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1777558268
OL,3,CKnow the sun and know your skin:
OL,4,CPublic health warnings amidst high UV
OL,5,Clevels
OL,7,FMartin explains: "It's about taking
OL,8,Fadvantage of the interactions (these
OL,9,Fprofessionals) have with islanders to
OL,10,Fencourage early detection,
OL,11,Fparticularly for the malignant skin
OL,12,Fcancers which are really quite
OL,13,Faggressive and can have a significant
OL,14,Fimpact on people's lives".
OL,16,FPublic Health authorities advise the
OL,17,Ffollowing to prevent sun damage:
OL,19,FThe following could also help identify
OL,20,Fpossible signs of melanoma:
OL,26,@pD@_pmqD@Npn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G10/11
